{"tid":226963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"中學畢業之後仲點樣識到男女朋友？","createTime":"2017-05-02T21:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T09:49:53.000Z","uid":9287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64bd68a8c486073614a2d6f3c2e014464aefffa9","tid":226963,"uid":9287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:38:29.000Z","msg":"中學嘅時候最純樸<br />\n上到大學，好多人都開始戴上面具，真正熟嘅朋友真係唔多，其他新識嘅開始熟又完Sem<br />\n除非住hall，如果唔係都keep唔住一段長久嘅關係<br />\n莫講話出黎做野，一堆堆做唔完嘅野都唔得閒去結識另一半<br />\n<br />\n講真中學無拍過拖/中學拍拖嘅嗰個上到大學先散真係好遺憾<br />\n<br />\n同咗中學一齊到而家4年嘅女朋友講咗分手已經有年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜闌人靜，好空虛好寂莫<br />\n<br />\n中學畢業之後仲點樣識到另一半？一齊得長唔長久？"},{"pid":"4c093f8f2937098613514c3834224abcb9f3e32c","tid":226963,"uid":9287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbeab05dd2f385a13cff6a3f7332dd4a45016e2c","tid":226963,"uid":9287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想拍拖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28acf94ec2c4225b49ec535d77a4fdb531582b68","tid":226963,"uid":113604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:00:06.000Z","msg":"上網 交友app/打機<br />\n大學上下莊住下hall<br />\n<br />\n利申 中學拍拖入到大學散左 入左大學年半後遇到而家個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15cefb13796cbda925b58c5850d6542dbe155ee","tid":226963,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:01:03.000Z","msg":"番工創業食秘書姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf70d7903d3ba05300a0783d4ddf0d2580c9944","tid":226963,"uid":9287,"l